{{Quote|Han Solo, last of the red-hot space-smugglers&hellip;,&hellip;going soft over a girl not much bigger than a Wodanian wood-sprite!|Amaiza Foxtrain|<ref name="Marvel 9">[[Star Wars (1977) 9|''Star Wars'' (1977) 9]]</ref> }}
'''Wodanian wood-sprites''' were tiny beings with which [[Amaiza Foxtrain/Legends|Amaiza Foxtrain]] was familiar. She claimed that [[Merri Shen Doshun]] was only slightly larger than the species.<ref name="Marvel 9" /> They were from [[Wodan system/Legends|Wodan]], a [[Planet/Legends|planet]] located within the Rifle Worlds of the [[Hapes Cluster/Legends|Hapes Cluster]].<ref name="The Essential Atlas">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Wodanian wood-sprites were created by [[Roy Thomas]] and were mentioned in the dialog of [[Star Wars (1977) 9|''Star Wars'' (1977) 9]], published in [[1978]]. ''[[The Essential Atlas]]'', published in [[2009]], created a planet based on this name.

